Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…女生套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然就為了這餐把我拉來餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天的女生套餐實在是好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小京真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京  你打麻將的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才剛記住全部的役就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…討厭麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咲  你會打麻將嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是會…但是我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和家裡人打麻將  總是輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲做什麼都不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總比少個人要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便陪陪我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不夠的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…不夠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊校舍的樓頂有部門活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  小京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎  公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了個冤大頭來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小京  我都說了我討厭麻將了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼  你認識和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才在橋附近讀書的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然互相認識那就好說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是去年的全國中學生大會的優勝者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在學校餐廳買了墨西哥餅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是墨西哥餅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會拿你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去倒茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和真的很厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在去年的全國中學生大會獲得優勝的最強中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且父母是檢事與律師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受男生們歡迎喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和某人大不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就我們幾個來下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說要下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢…那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始點25000  計分點30000  沒有順位加減得點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  和家人以外的人打還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混一色  2000點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常會點炮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不很容易就看出在做筒子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是初學者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～立直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我點和了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你捨棄三色三同順想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託您的福  我是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～進入下一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  咲的麻將真是不怎麼出彩啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點數倒像是會計算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下起雨來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒帶傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我中學時的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫宮永咲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是竹井久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個學校我不是學生會長而是學生議會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是麻將部的部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上的牌不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷幺九 平和 三色三同順  最少也有7700點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  宮永咲  就是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯報點數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸九萬  扔掉六萬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要故意去掉斷幺九與三色三同順來降低點數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九萬也不是危險牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是小和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學的點數是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是正負0點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回連續正負0點！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長醒了人數也湊齊了  我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去圖書館還書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得很匆忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為小和太強了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓倒性的勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓倒性的勝利？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼傻話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著她的點數就沒什麼注意到的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學的點數是三回連續正負0點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要說這是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能  碰巧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將受運氣影響很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專業的也不過第一位確率在30%左右就算很強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說正負0點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比贏還要難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還連續三回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得不可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有壓倒性的力量差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是怎麼了  突然跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩  能不能進我們部呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那樣算上真子就五個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們部  說不定能進軍全國哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回連續正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要那麼打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是在和家人打麻將時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的話就拿不到點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直贏的話也會被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中  就變成這種打法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再與我打一局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每回打出正負0點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類能做到的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不打了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己再也不打了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲  洗澡要洗到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在從早上起就吃便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了哦  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似有個每回都以正負0點和的一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  消息真靈通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  和贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏是贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自尊方面會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下卷被借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼被借走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生議會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼在意小細節啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這書我有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全集都有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我借你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我對宮永同學有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心上人來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須賀同學  把優希叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這樣啊  這個文學少女就是那個正負0點的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才發現啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希  人齊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  馬上去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學  和  真子  還有優希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小咲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四個人進行二回戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我上的話大家就都沒得玩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是東風戰  赤牌四張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這還算是麻將部員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來解說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的麻將多為半莊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從東一局到南四局為止打8局的是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而東風戰則又是其一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從東一局到東四局  只進行四局比賽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  就是說所需時間變為一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有所謂的赤牌是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被塗紅的5的牌  赤牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次有四張這樣的牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶牌有…8張？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種恐怖的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始點25000 計分點30000對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了書  約好只下兩回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長給了我機會  今天從一開始就要認真去打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲還是要打出正負0點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照一般的想法  每回正負0點是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天還是帶赤牌的東風短期決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看吧  你的真正的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊家  立直  上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二巡  一點也看不透她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚～立直一發自摸加三張寶牌  莊家跳滿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看看這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希的過去平均獲得點數圖表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東場是很能賺點數啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是到了南場就會失去勢頭變弱的類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但集中力無法持續就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易厭煩才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8300點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是染谷學姐扔掉的牌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣前進喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希那傢伙  想逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  情況變的有意思了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷幺九平和加兩張寶牌  11600點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就連莊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的規則是百位上的點數以五捨六入來算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要達成正負0點的話  點數就要在29600點到30500點之間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸  門前清混一色紅中役牌加一張寶牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒家3000  莊家6000  每人再加一本場100分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～我不想聽那樣長長的咒文了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  本想只是看看情況的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  最後一局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是咲的門前清混一色聽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能點和的話就是5200點  正好正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從優希那裡直接拿來的話  就能一舉成為第一了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一巡的赤五筒也不要！？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中一點也沒有勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用優希的五筒來和的話  貌似可以正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣就會因為第一而追加點數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用和的赤五筒來和的話  順位雖然沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻會變成滿貫而無法達成正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩除了正負0點什麼也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學應該是想達成5200點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直棒出來的話  會如何做呢
